Corrected Ukrainian translation of the unit.

As Kraken has fought in Kharkiv Oblast, and fighting in the vicinity of Luhansk in Novoselesivske and other towns such as Bilohorivka, have been included either as part of the Battle of Donbas in 2022, or the Luhansk Oblast campaign from 2022 to present. Therefore, both of these engagements have been listed on this page due to the aforementioned reasons, and the involvement of Kraken fighters in these areas. Both have been sourced properly to reinforce these changes.

Additional reference on the size of the unit, mentioning that 600 Kharkiv residents banded together to form the unit in the early days of the invasion. This would make sense as by 27 Feb 2022, they would go on to expand to approximately 1,500 fighters.
